<div tiddler="NewJournalMacro" modifier="JeremyRuston" modified="200608191715" created="200608191355" tags="macros">The {{{&lt;&lt;newJournal&gt;&gt;}}} macro creates a new tiddler with it's title set to the current date, and the cursor in the body text area ready to type.\n\nThis macro is identical to the NewTiddlerMacro except that the &quot;title&quot; parameter is treated as a DateFormatString so that you can specify your own date format.</div>
